{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316620/extras/storepage_logo_demo_616w.png?t=1734598592\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Easy to pick up and play, with infinite depth to master -\u00a0</i>TopplePOP</strong> is physics puzzle action!\u00a0 1-4 players guide bendy animal acrobats on rubber bands in a race to rescue their pals.\u00a0 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DEMO includes:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Story</i></strong>  - 3 chapters from the full solo/co-op Campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Battle</i></strong> - 2 AI opponents from the full Tournament</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Party </i></strong><strong>-</strong>\u00a01 &quot;Classic&quot; Mix  for infinite puzzles in 2 zones: <strong><i>City</i></strong> and <strong><i>Stadium</i></strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Challenges</i></strong>\u00a0- 5 zen puzzles refreshed weekly, with speedrun leaderboards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> <br>FEATURES:\u00a0</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use Keys + Mouse or Controller (recommended)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1 - 4 Players </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">local multiplayer,\u00a0 online multiplayer\u00a0 or  both at once!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solo / Co-op Story &amp; Battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">PvE against AI opponents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">PvP - 1v1,\u00a0 2v2 Teams,\u00a0 3 to 4 Player free-for-all.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Casual Parties and Spectacular eSports Tournaments!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weekly Leaderboard Challenges</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>( * local multiplayer requires at least 1 controller )</i>    </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><stron